Class RuleGrounding

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.domains.rules.RuleGrounding
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RuleGrounding.Failed

    public class RuleGrounding
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a set of possible groundings for a rule
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  RuleGrounding.Failed
      Special type of rule grounding when the grounding has "failed", i.e. there is no possible assignment of values for the condition(s).
